// Stage 3: sub_match and match_results.
// Ported from libc++ include/regex lines 4180–4880 (sub_match, its comparison
// operator set, match_results and its members).  The regex engine itself
// (basic_regex, regex_match/search/replace, the iterators) is not ported yet;
